name: Stay Clean - Quitting Smoke App
description:
This is a UI Design for quitting addiction from substance like nicotine etc. This UI provide some functions like track your mood through the day, how many days you've been stay clean, how much money you owned just by quitting substances, and achievements to keep stay clean, etc.


This UI Design also have micro interactions like launch screen and button.
